Source.Name: rocmlir
Source.Summary: MLIR-based convolution and GEMM kernel generator for ROCm
Source.Description: rocMLIR is a MLIR-based convolution and GEMM kernel generator targetting AMD hardware. This generator is mainly used from MIOpen and MIGraphX, but it can be used on a standalone basis.
